<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3943947>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Procamallanus (Spirocamallanus) tomsici sp. nov. a: Male, anterior end, lateral view. b: Female, anterior end, lateral view. c: Female, apical view. d: Male, head, lateral view. e: Female, head, lateral view. f: Female, vulva, lateral view. g: Larva. h: Female, tail, lateral view. i: Male, posterior end with spicules, lateral view. j: Male, posterior end with spicules and papillae, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3943947/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3943949>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Procamallanus (Spirocamallanus) tomsici sp. nov. (SEM micrographs) a: Female, cephalic end. Six pores (discontinuous white arrows), amphids (discontinuous black arrow), papillae (black arrows). Scale=3 µm. b: Deirid. Scale= 1 µm. c: Female, vulva, subventral view. Scale=30 µm. Lateral cuticular ornamentation. (White arrows) d: Female, cuticular ornamentation, lateral view (white arrows). Scale=10µm. e: Female, anus, lateral-ventral view. Scale=10µm. f: Female, posterior end, lateral-dorsal view. Scale=6 µm. g: Male, posterior end, ventral view. Scale=10µm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3943949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

